<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error <%= status || '500' %> | Imperio</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/warhammer-style.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8em;
            color: var(--mechanicus-red);
            margin: 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(128, 0, 0, 0.7);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: var(--imperial-gold);
        }
        
        .error-details {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            border: 1px solid var(--imperial-gold);
            text-align: left;
            max-height: 300px;
            overflow-y: auto;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: var(--parchment);
        }
        
        .skull-icon {
            font-size: 4em;
            color: var(--imperial-gold);
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.6);
        }
        
        .back-button {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Administración del Imperio</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Adeptus Administratum - Servicio de Errores</div>
    </header>
    
    <div class="container error-container">
        <div class="skull-icon">☠</div>
        
        <h2 class="error-code"><%= status || '500' %></h2>
        
        <div class="error-message">
            <%= message || 'Error interno del servidor' %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="imperial-quote">
            "Hasta en el fallo, hay servicio al Emperador. Aprende de los errores o enfréntate a la purga."
        </div>
        
        <% if (process.env.NODE_ENV === 'development' && error) { %>
            <div class="error-details">
                <strong>Detalles del error (solo visible en desarrollo):</strong><br>
                <%= error.stack || error %>
            </div>
        <% } %>
        
        <a href="/" class="imperial-button back-button">Volver al Inicio</a>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <p>Por la gloria del Emperador de la Humanidad | Adeptus Administratum &copy; 41st Milenio</p>
        <p>Sanctioned by the Inquisition</p>
    </footer>
    
    <script src="/js/warhammer-scripts.js"></script>
</body>
</html>